        <p>Once integrated, Streamlyne analyzes millions of data points in real time to build a tailored predictive analytics system for your plant. Managers and operators are able to monitor current DCS alarms and build custom multi-sensor scenarios to recognize critical events (flaring, hydrates, pipeline leaks, etc.) before they happen.
