        <p>Streamlyne monitors real-time sensor data to detect existing DCS alarms along with custom multi-sensor Streamlyne alarms. All alarms can have custom causes and solutions built in that can be selected or entered as each alarm occurs. This helps with cataloguing experienced operator knowledge to be used later in high stress situations.
